OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FAndy Burnham's allies believe his
OL,7,Fvictory gives him the huge vote of
OL,8,Fconfidence to challenge Keir Starmer
OL,9,Ffor the Labour leadership. Political
OL,10,FCorrespondent Harry Horton reports
OL,11,Ffrom the count in Makerfield
OL,13,FAndy Burnham has won the Makerfield by-
OL,14,Felection by 9,231 votes, marking his
OL,15,Freturn to Westminster and paving the
OL,16,Fway for a potential leadership
OL,17,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
