OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FThe Greater Manchester mayor won more
OL,7,Fthan half of all votes cast in the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election, comfortably
OL,9,Fbeating the combined total for second
OL,10,Fand third place parties Reform UK and
OL,11,FRestore Britain.
OL,13,FReform candidate Rob Kenyon won 34.5%
OL,14,Fof the vote, while Restore Britain's
OL,15,FRebecca Shepherd won 6.8%, which
OL,16,Ftogether come to 41.3%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
