OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FConservative candidate Michael
OL,7,FWinstanley won 2.2% of the vote in
OL,8,FMakerfield ` the Tories' second lowest
OL,9,Fshare of the vote at a Westminster by-
OL,10,Felection since the Second World War.
OL,12,FThe turnout in Makerfield was 58.7%,
OL,13,Fthe highest for a parliamentary by-
OL,14,Felection in nearly seven years.
OL,16,FBurnham said he wanted to ensure
OL,17,FMakerfield was synonymous with
OL,18,F"bringing about the change this
OL,19,Fcountry needs, bringing back something
OL,20,Fwe've lost ` hope ` hope for the
OL,21,Ffuture.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
