OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,F"I am proud that this place has shone
OL,7,Fin the world's spotlight for the last
OL,8,Ffew weeks, and the warmth, humour and
OL,9,Fhospitality of its people has been on
OL,10,Fshow for all to see. It will never be
OL,11,Fa stepping stone to me, but instead
OL,12,Fwill be my touchstone.
OL,14,F"A Makerfield test at the heart of
OL,15,FBritish politics will make sure that
OL,16,Fthe places Westminster has neglected
OL,17,Fwill now get fairness."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@WO]
