OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FThe Labour Party has retained the seat
OL,7,Fafter former MP Josh Simons stepped
OL,8,Fdown in May to make way for Burnham's
OL,9,Freturn to Westminster.
OL,11,FCabinet minister Lisa Nandy said it
OL,12,Fwas "history in the making" after Andy
OL,13,FBurnham won the Makerfield by-election.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
