OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FShe said: "What Andy's shown here is
OL,7,Fthat there is something that he
OL,8,Fbrings, a willingness to go out and
OL,9,Ffight for the change that people need,
OL,10,Fto take on any system and any person
OL,11,Fwho stands in the way and to be bold
OL,12,Fand to wear his heart on his sleeve,
OL,13,Fand people have responded.
OL,15,F"I think that with him back in the top
OL,16,Fteam, at the top table, helping to
OL,17,Fdrive that change, I think we'll be in
OL,18,Fa really strong position."
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOUzD@ZO]
