OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBurnham will now step down from this
OL,12,Frole to take up his seat in the House
OL,13,Fof Commons.
OL,15,FHis return is highly likely to trigger
OL,16,Fa leadership contest within the Labour
OL,17,FParty, but there is no timetable set
OL,18,Ffor when this challenge might be.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
