OL,3,CAndy Burnham's Makerfield win piles
OL,4,Cpressure on Keir Starmer
OL,6,FMakerfield has seen a seismic by-
OL,7,Felection with the focus being split
OL,8,Fbetween local representation and a
OL,9,Fpotential new prime minister.
OL,11,FSpeaking earlier this week, Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer, who has been increasingly
OL,13,Funpopular among voters and his own
OL,14,Fparty, said he wanted Burnham to win
OL,15,Fand, if he is successful, will offer
OL,16,Fhim a big role in government. Burnham,
OL,17,Fhowever, has already declined this
OL,18,Foffer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
